      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, primarily for parts or as a significant restoration project. The engine and transmission require major repairs, and there are visible signs of heavy wear, including body rust and a degraded interior. While it is not currently suitable for daily driving, it could serve as a donor car for someone with the right tools and expertise. Please expect to tow this vehicle from its current location.",
