    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s officially time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It looks and drives just like it did the day I got it. No scratches, no weird smells, and the interior is spotless. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 45500.0,
