    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with its 8,000 RPM redline and six individual throttle bodies. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring peak valvetrain timing and long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a speed-sensitive variable M differential lock. The chassis maintains factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by pristine bushings and untouched suspension geometry. This is a mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist seeking a true analog driving experience.",
